commit.message:
PolicykitAgent: Set completed of new authentication

..when other one in progress already

Notify the polkit, that we can't do next authentication if one is
already in progress. This prevents the initial caller to possibly wait
indefinetly for the authentication.
Prevent multiple "authentication already in progress" dialogs.

verification.payload:
